uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"唉我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96839c64b1437d4a41b87e727168988300066127","tid":220960,"uid":92634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有時會失眠到好燥好焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友話買唔知咩敏感藥或者感冒藥，輕劑量嗰種，會有少少睡意，但唔敢亂試"},{"pid":"25d4c57edaef8a1cc4faa7c3b8798e003da19006","tid":220960,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"12點幾1點上床訓<br />\n要攤到3點幾先訓到<br />\n日日都係咁 算唔算失眠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二朝逼自己10點幾起身<br />\n因為唔想下一晚訓都訓唔到"},{"pid":"5d9ddc3c6622aaaecaf57ce0c938887f987037b6","tid":220960,"uid":92634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過原因係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n壓力大嘅話，我食過巴哈甜睡寧，都okay work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d49b2ef6f5b9ae2626a2a62447c20d2455c1d5","tid":220960,"uid":84431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試吓日頭做啲令自己好攰嘅嘢<br />\n例如做運動<br />\n咁會易啲瞓着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋臨瞓前嗰半個鐘唔好做啲要用專注力嘅嘢<br />\n例如玩手機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:成日失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以為我自己回post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係咁諗 但試過做齊哂都係失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我有時就算係好攰都照失眠<br />\n可能因為嗰排多嘢煩<br />\n咁呢啲就另一回事<br />\n係心病<br />\n要解決咗煩緊嗰件事先瞓得着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e493274131e0e66d0ce22753cf44c1c34f7c987","tid":220960,"uid":79987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:18:02.000Z","msg":"訓係到會好強心跳"},{"pid":"fa81dcfd40f4eac97f4a769a71f2c260bd0bc3b4","tid":220960,"uid":35293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"早過12 點訓既話，次次唔夠3 個鐘就會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失敗多年，個人殘左好多好多"},{"pid":"f98c681d14738196db776848f75eb895a09ad3eb","tid":220960,"uid":103172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"經常失眠<br />\n做其他嘢做到眼瞓先停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159bc33a362c331862d42053d1ac004314c5d57c","tid":220960,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"睇下d唔明又興趣既書+聽Delta Wave"},{"pid":"c0b0e527d66202571b0fbc44d840a3831b2ee90f","tid":220960,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下d唔明又<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>興趣既書+聽Delta Wave</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d95c1bb28e2da88d06c803d9c98c07eef905ed","tid":220960,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"睇醫生叫佢俾安眠藥"}]}